source.name: Polling Places in Washington DC
source.description: District of Columbia Polling Places. This dataset contains points representing locations of polling places, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.
